Overview

_Gex is a structured, deterministic AI code execution engine designed
for safe, reviewable, and controlled code modification.

It enables:
- Surgical code transformations using structured patch formats
- File-by-file execution with streaming results
- Human-in-the-loop approval workflows
- Safe execution via isolated working copies

